                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The wereshark critically hit with a trident Strike on their most recent action this turn</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The wereshark digs their trident deep within their target, skewering it before taking a massive bite. The target of the Strike becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Escape] DC 18) and takes @Damage[1d4[bleed]] damage, and the wereshark attempts a jaws Strike against it. The wereshark can't use their trident while they have a creature grabbed with it, but they can pull the trident free with a single action that has the manipulate trait.</p>"
                },
